                        This project commenced with a condense investigation into the existing system
                        to find problems at hand and then to propose a solution to the problem. There
                        was also literature review to acquire more knowledge from other people work,
                        which helped to enhance the development of the system.
                        The project main objective which was achieved using a high level language and
                        a relational database management system (JAVA and MYSQL) to create a web
                        based application that provide the patients, where they can be diagnosed with all
                        qualification provided.</p>
                        <p>The system could be used majorly in the following areas such as<p>
