                        </ol>
                        <p>The system was also designed to ease the stress involved in disease diagnosis. Most
                        importantly is that the system is fast and it helps to reduce error as regards to
                        
                        every patient?s information. The system will also ease the work of the medical
                        administration.</p>
                        <p>This web based system is designed for people who cannot afford to visit
                        hospitals. For the past few years, the number of online disease diagnosis system
                        has increased rapidly. This particular project deals with the problem of disease
                        diagnosis and drug prescription for Malaria and Typhoid.</p>

                        <p>This system is recommended for all hospitals and pharmaceutical outlets. It will
